{"tid":1614210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新計劃！焚書坑儒三中商！速入！幫手推推推","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T00:54:51.000Z","uid":205792,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92c5d341f29a7103afd730432997a851d6f785f2","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，小弟用個標題水左大家入黎.<br />\n<br />\n事先聲明 前線乜決定都唔割！齊上齊落！<br />\n但係提醒：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得賣港商店懲罰佢無乜所謂.<br />\n但係要好似下面個po位巴打咁講合乎比例原則.<br />\n唔好通通都幫佢裝修.<br />\n<br />\n破壞商舖請合乎比例原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另外，我覺得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">書店真係不宜用水法火魔</span>就算係三中商都係咁話.<br />\n<br />\n你裝修出賣手足既食肆，損失利益既持份者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Only係佢間公司</span></span>，達到直接經濟制裁既效果. 抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞書店會整爛好多書，依啲書所牽涉既持份者係廣大既作者！無論黃藍都有！水淹大軍 火燒群書 只係會全部書攬炒！香港、台灣、外國不同作者既書都會受影響！你估下佢哋見到自己既書咁樣既時候會點諗？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>經濟制裁唔係問題，但係要好似對準政權咁！對準商家！唔好搞到自己友！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可能你會話：屌你老母我地罷買三中商咪又會損害到黃作者既利益 咪一鳩樣！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我可以同你講！絕對唔同！<br />\n你試諗下，邊有一個創作人想見到自己辛辛苦苦創造出黎既作品俾人搞？<br />\n個個都當本書係自己既仔，係心血結晶。<br />\n無一位創作人會想見到自己創作出黎既作品俾人燒/浸爛，就算係自己友都一樣！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins>罷買，取代燒書浸書<br />\n</ins></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家咁熱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去幫佢哋裝修下玻璃算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無左塊玻璃 我相信佢都幾難開鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins>光復香港 時代革命</ins></em></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f489a31a1a4e10c2d24a13e24350b8060c4ee547","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"p牌仔開po 準備定屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0094ea5dd7aaab205850f437309f8792f13745ac","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"2458b2b6ba95af8e4111d853b9a7f1e391e36f38","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"06753b657099754b89ea2b4c25c54bc8284835d3","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"05627c3f0016747f867bf17b513568987bcd6a75","tid":1614210,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"129fd3c1ef5425db7e8b074d430532ade06e4bfd","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ec07611a8e8192dfc352545d842301d9c89c58e5","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9f923b23f6d3eac3cd8e35e621f7b3f8983ea7da","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"4e6ea2cb0d556cbd741722699b9ee6e425ee9633",