,"msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ae6b3bb46253fcc287c3a6bd686c091338994d","tid":1614210,"uid":205792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50d123130931d6993aa3def18a3bbec10c9f582c","tid":1614210,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:54:51.000Z","msg":"罷買三中商都要比地方人哋買書㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[香港本土書店List]裝飾罷買三中商，中共思想控制香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}